-- HK Secretary of Transport May Not Join New Government, Says RTHK
-- B y   W e n d y   M o c k
-- 2012-05-08T12:32:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-08/hk-secretary-of-transport-may-not-join-new-government-says-rthk.html
Secretary for transport and housing,
 Eva Cheng , indicated that she will not join Hong Kong’s new
government,  Radio Television Hong Kong  reported today. She told
reporters that her family is her top priority at the moment,
according to the report.  Hong Kong’s chief executive elect Leung Chun-ying begins a
five-year term on July 1.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Wendy Mock in Hong Kong at 
 wmock3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
